            <lg xml:id="TK1230">
<l>poruṇmālai yāḷarai yuḷḷi maruṇmālai</l>
<l>māyumeṉ māyā vuyir</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My (hitherto) unextinguished life is now lost in this bewildering night at the thought of him who has the nature of wealth.</l>
